construct: The Construct is the base building block for the TechnoMages.
Constructs act like programmable building blocks that utilise the reconstructive power of nanites.

When a certain combination of resources are placed within the construct, the internal nanites will identify the pattern and get to work by breaking down the construct and items into their base components, before reconstructing as the desired block.
